{"tid":2100049,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【集思廣益】如果大部份香港人要集中移民去一個地方建市，邊度最好？","createTime":"2020-07-08T17:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T14:56:05.000Z","uid":54684,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60755dcae796cbd62c6f8f823975a8b7c8087547","tid":2100049,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"依家好多海外重建香港 / 海外社區 / 海外議會既構想，構建國際香港網絡<br />\n人多先有power，先鞏固到身份同文化<br />\n但係其實邊度最好？有無共識？<br />\n<br />\n1. 澳洲西北<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8AgVGw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8AgVGw.png&h=9c92d782&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n+8時區<br />\n鄰近東南亞人口密集地區<br />\n與澳洲本身最繁榮既東南部相對，減少競爭<br />\n溫度合宜<br />\n回歸前有人提出係達爾文建港<br />\n<br />\n2. 加拿大西岸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHRLO18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHRLO18.png&h=5562e751&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n鄰近現成港人社區，有支援，但藍絲廢老眾多<br />\n加拿大地大人少，亟需發展<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\n3. 加拿大東岸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KK6DpBa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKK6DpBa.png&h=fb0fa967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多倫多工作機會較多<br />\n生活成本較高<br />\n<br />\n4. 美國兩岸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgMWVJm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgMWVJm.png&h=04e0012e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7fkCWH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7fkCWH.png&h=587e0dfc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n附近人煙倜密，高度發展，或不易有機會去發展<br />\n<br />\n5. 英國蘇格蘭 / 北愛爾蘭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BW0ddvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBW0ddvp.png&h=ffcce2c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回歸前有人提出係當地建港<br />\n附近已高度發展<br />\n<br />\n6. 福克蘭群島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PmJRKCq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPmJRKCq.png&h=5dcea494&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n山卡啦，無人同你爭，有人口需求<br />\n無咩發展空間<br />\n<br />\n7. 打散，各有各移民，不建港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s97yXXF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs97yXXF.jpg&h=2a3998c4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n各走他鄉，融入當地，如泥牛入海，同化成當地人，放棄語言文化<br />\n<br />\n最後quote沈旭暉一句︰<br />\n「要移民的人你不用鼓勵也會走，假如真的要走，也依靠網絡維繫香港人社區，把資金、能力去中央化，化整為零，繼續支持留在香港的真香港人，大家才能構成一個整體。<em><span class=\"blue\">別像上一代消極地到溫哥華成為唐人街廢老</span></em>。」<br />\n你點睇？"},{"pid":"7b7c6bd6cae7abd37f69d4920dcb66ddcd549bf7","tid":2100049,"uid":273703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"038ae97c66dc6cbce4cc98c17f279a4c59a17ab5","tid":2100049,"uid":171506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"加拿大西岸好<br />\n<br />\n已有港人社區<br />\n無多倫多咁涷<br />\n加人相對友善"},{"pid":"bdd91af24f49217e1c0452bd00dd527acd45b198","tid":2100049,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5993d4e3d0cc81dc3dda8dacbf80e5e48ae4e4e2","tid":2100049,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:13:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acc47d95b883e8f7bb3fde23475e3e7baa89894c","tid":2100049,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"初選宣傳不足，快閃文宣開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2100039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2100039</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"958006983da161fe9d53f6f28af65cf1acd48b5c","tid":2100049,"uid":294667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:43:02.000Z","msg":"UK Isle of Wight 同對岸地方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwaQf1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwaQf1M.jpg&h=eba1c62c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"586326217a8be04bd4dee925392bac65bbb094ed","tid":2100049,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038a6b6d757e00f7f82b838c13e6d827b7d53011","tid":2100049,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"加西<br />\n天氣同香港差唔多<br />\n加拿大人比較友善<br />\n政府政策算開放<br />\n需然稅重但福利算唔差<br />\n最重要係多啲香港人去平衡番班藍屍"},{"pid":"0aea84262defda206c4467fb43b65512bacec8d6","tid":2100049,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}